718889f-b.title: Manhattan: Church Street - Franklin Street
718889f-b.text:
(1)
Church Street, west side, north from and including Franklin, to and
including White Streots. Also shown (across clearance for Sixth Ave.,
Extension), is White Street, at and adjoining the N.:. corner of Church
Street.
September 12, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.  NE,. 4430
(2)
The same, a closer view.
September 12, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
